# PoolTool 2026 frontend — API and WebSocket (no hardcoded IPs)
# Default: same host as the page on port 3004 (e.g. https://www.pooltool.io → api at www.pooltool.io:3004).
# For production build when API is on a different host (e.g. api.pooltool.io), set:
#
# Dev server on same machine as API (e.g. npm run serve on the server):
# VUE_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:3004
# VUE_APP_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3004/ws
#
# API on another host:
# VUE_APP_API_URL=http://YOUR_API_HOST:3004
# VUE_APP_WS_URL=ws://YOUR_API_HOST:3004/ws
#
# For HTTPS: use https:// and wss://
